<h1>Welcome to Journalizer</h1>

<p>Hi<%= @user.display_name.present? ? " #{@user.display_name.split.first}" : "" %>!</p>

<p>Thanks for signing up. Journalizer makes it easy to digitize your handwritten journal entries using AI-powered transcription.</p>

<p><strong>Here's how to get started:</strong></p>

<ol style="padding-left: 20px; color: #555;">
  <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Take photos of your journal pages or upload existing images</li>
  <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Review and confirm your upload</li>
  <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Our AI will transcribe your handwriting and organize entries by date</li>
</ol>

<p><a href="<%= dashboard_url %>" class="btn">Go to Dashboard</a></p>

<p class="muted">Questions or feedback? Just reply to this email.</p>
